com.b2international.commons.dynamic

Interface DynamicList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DynamicMap, DynamicValue
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynamicListImpl

    public interface DynamicList
extends DynamicMap
    Represents an immutable list that associates non-negative integer indexes with DynamicValues. Can also be viewed as a map where only numeric keys are permitted.
